  Then for any set <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>, there is a function <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> with <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {dom}(f) = A]]></fr:tex> such that
  <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[     f(a) = b \Leftrightarrow  \varphi (a,b).   ]]></fr:tex></fr:p>
    
      
